Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.76,0:17:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一鼓作氣衝進去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.47,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,過來了 有意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,敵方Knightmare一架 正以高速侵入進來
