Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.81,0:19:15.52,Default,,0,0,0,,混賬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.56,0:19:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不好了 阿基德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,被突破了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,夏英格卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.86,0:19:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,我要殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.74,0:19:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,黃泉之國中你的同伴在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.61,0:19:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我來給你踐行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.41,0:19:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.42,0:19:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿修雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.37,0:19:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,你靠太近了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥 戰鬥有什麼意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,毀滅這個世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,就是我的目的 阿基德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.60,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,去死 阿基德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,毀滅世界 去死吧
